INVESTMENTS AND INTERSEGMENT ELIMINATIONS. ADDITIONALLY, OPERATING INCOME UNDER ELIMINATIONS/OTHER FOR THE FISCAL YEAR ENDED JANUARY 28, 2007 INCLUDES $129 MILLION

OF COST ASSOCIATED WITH EXECUTIVE SEVERANCE AND SEPARATION AGREEMENTS. THE FOLLOWING TABLES PRESENT FINANCIAL INFORMATION BY SEGMENT FOR THE FISCAL YEARS ENDED JANUARY 28, 2007,

